      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHOT OF WHISKY (1) has the advantage of a nice draw for her first outing. Can get off the mark here. TOO MUCH WHISKY (2) is a first starter by Hooked On Scotch out of Fire On Ice with no trial form to work with. Profiles well but prefer to see a move in betting. BALMAIN BOY (3) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at his last four runs. Last start finished 2nd in a Maiden on June 2 over 457m at this track behind Son Of Rupee beaten 1.3 lengths (26.03). Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Overdue and is among the main hopes. CANYA DESTROY (8) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can make amends.",
